cdata.name: Cardstack
cdata.desc:
Cardstackis a decentralized platform that aims to make blockchainusable and scalable for the mass market. At this platform, users can be provided with a feature named CardstackFramework, a comprehensive SDK to create card-based blockchainapps.

CARD is an Ethereum based token developed by Cardstackto be a medium of exchange within the platform. It will be used to reward open-source developers, also, CARD holders can become miners to validate transactions and earn fees.
